Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:52.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:03.43,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and crew reached Fishman Island,\Nlocated 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates,\Nwho are plotting to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,alongside Vander Decken, who is after\NMermaid Princess Shirahoshi, move in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats find themselves\Ncaught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro, Usopp and Brook have been\Ncaptured by Hody at Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She broke... She broke my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What don't I just destroy everything altogether?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, he gave me a lot of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Hachi, Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Megalo!
