Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We are almost at the plaza! Hurry up, Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Father-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm here-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Jinbe-sama! Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm here-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna see the Princess get hurt, freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's take her!
