Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have quite an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What a view!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Mamboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Ryuboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Fukaboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the pirates manage that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princes were winning by far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, the tables have turned against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanna fight some more-zugon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Much! Don't get so heated up! Or I'm gonna become a piece of dried squid-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers of the army. The ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And the royal family. There is no one left in this country, who can fight us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What unbelievable power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be! Those powers are fake-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't really matter if it enables them to take over the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Hody, let's put them to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--Burn them alive! --No, impale them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish a terrible death on those who lack pride and look to coexist with the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard from Decken's crew yet, with regards to Shirahoshi's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no point in doing this if we can't lure her here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything to our sister! She won't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't harm you in any way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that I don't know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the Mermaid with that troublesome power so I want to be rid of her the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We got them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi and Jinbe got caught in a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Father-sama! Brothers-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How lucky I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We caught the two that I concerned about most, all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too good to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I am very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't have to go through this if I hadn't been fooled...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's done is done so never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here as I thought, Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked you back when you were a wild man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you, Hody? You look so different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Boss Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he left the island after he quit the Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Princess Shirahoshi had been kidnapped by Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Boss Jinbe rescue her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone that I wanted to see is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was easier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My only concern now is what the Straw Hats will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I assume they're desperately looking for a way in to the Ryugu Palace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they make it here after they find their friends dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we're totally ready to ambush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 30,000 human slaves we've caught in the sea over the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And 70,000 Fishmen who know how to use arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They moved here from the closed Fishman District.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...100,000 outlaws altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a few female and child slaves who can't fight, outside the plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We will take care of them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll soon have more human slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, 100,000 of you islanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools are a dishonor to our race so vacate your houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can either drop dead or run. Think about what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Horsing around in public... You kids have no class at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you for a long time. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to say one thing to you since you're at the height of your glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Sharley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:13:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my prevision, a man will destroy Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it me that you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who will destroy the island is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell what the Straw Hat boy will do specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My point is that it's not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who determines the fate of Fishman Island is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...not you, Hody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! Madame's previsions are accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Hody will never reign over the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Sharley!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--Madame! --How could he do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that, Sharley? What do you have against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:15:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I was a kid, everybody in the Fishman District
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,may have looked up to your brother Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But then we seized power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the name "Arlong Pirates" is nothing but a symbol to unite us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even need the name "Arlong" anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The only man who can break the whole country to its foundation and rebuild it, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...me! Because I have enough power to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how powerful I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the power that I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I started this whole thing 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:16:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Concerning the late Queen of the Ryugu Kingdom, who you fools still love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Otohime was killed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the human then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you not notice it, idiots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The day before that fateful day 10 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...I would do anything if I can make some big money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this real money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a half of it. You can have the rest after you finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this is enough to drink all day for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so easy. Even a child can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However, don't let anyone notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--Put out the fire! --Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--Protect the royal family! --Put out the fire now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Otohime-sama has been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, give me the rest of that money now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I set fire to those signatures like you told me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna make a run for it already so give me the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...who killed our queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Otohime was killed by a human!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody got fooled completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! It was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She was annoying. Don't you think so, Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She begged everyone not to seek revenge against humans
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but to become friends with them instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She was bugging me because she almost accomplished her goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I wouldn't be satisfied with just killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, your mother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...someone who deserved death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such a thing to the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I came up with an idea to make the best of her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would allow me to stoke the hatred towards humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that citizens of Fishman Island once had
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroy the islanders' stupid dream along with Otohime - all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd point the finger at a human for killing Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I blamed it on a human, I knew that the islanders will get pissed off at humans again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it turned out that you all got fooled by my trick exactly as I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She was worth killing! Right, Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother was not murdered by a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I, her kinsman, did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:21:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I, standing in front of you now, killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I already knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, everyone on Fishman Island came together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and built a mysterious giant ship called Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason remains a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a leftover from the past now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me touch it with my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Decken, what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain of heartbreak will never go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wh-What's going on?! --Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm throwing the Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...at Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship is half the size of Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That means if it hits the island, not just Shirahoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but the whole island will be shattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't run or hide from me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:23:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi has no choice but to stay with me in my heart forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn in hell with the island! Goodbye my sweet Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi continues to fulfill her promise to her mother, Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody ridicules her and commences Neptune's execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The despairing citizens call out the name of their last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.13,0:23:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And their voice resounds throughout Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shirahoshi's Tears!\NLuffy Arrives at Last"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
